item.description:
Congressman Frank Guinta will be Speaking and doing our usual Q&A at our next regular meeting.  This will be your opportunity to hear what has really been happening in DC regarding the Debt Ceiling and so much more. I encurage everyone to attend and have your questions ready. Presidential hopeful Congressman Thadeus McCotter will also be attending this meeting and will hold a Q&A. No recordings are allowed without permission of Jerry DeLemus.

No videotaping or recording of this meeting without Prior approval by Jerry DeLemus
item.name: Congressman Frank Guinta and Pres. Candidate McCotter at our Regular 912 Meeting
